{"TopicId":197711,"ForumId":32,"TopicTitle":"Can you play KSP on mobile?","CreatedByName":"Spaceman50","CreatedById":207817,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-10-26T16:52:30Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Spaceman50","CreatedById":207817,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-10-26T16:52:30Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nCan you play KSP on mobile i mean i play it on my pc but i want to play it when i head to school\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222020-10-26T16:52:55Z\u0022 title=\u002210/26/2020 04:52  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00223 yr\u0022\u003EOctober 26, 2020\u003C/time\u003E by Spaceman50\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Vanamonde","CreatedById":27914,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-10-26T17:08:15Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nKSP does not have a mobile version. The simulation requires too much processing power.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Spacescifi","CreatedById":197504,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-10-26T17:14:57Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223873035\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022197711\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221603731150\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022207817\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Spaceman50\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n21 minutes ago, Spaceman50 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nCan you play KSP on mobile i mean i play it on my pc but i want to play it when i head to school\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nGive it time... the tech will catch up sooner or later.\n\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223873044\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022197711\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221603732095\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002227914\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Vanamonde\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n6 minutes ago, Vanamonde said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nKSP does not have a mobile version. The simulation requires too much processing power.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDitto.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"RealKerbal3x","CreatedById":183830,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-10-26T17:23:08Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223873044\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022197711\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221603732095\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002227914\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Vanamonde\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n11 minutes ago, Vanamonde said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nKSP does not have a mobile version. The simulation requires too much processing power.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223873050\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022197711\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221603732497\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022197504\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Spacescifi\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n4 minutes ago, Spacescifi said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nGive it time... the tech will catch up sooner or later.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAside from processing power, another issue is controls - how exactly are you going to fit all of KSP\u0027s controls onto a mobile phone screen?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/207817-spaceman50/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022207817\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/207817-spaceman50/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Spaceman50\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0I\u0027d recommend you check out Spaceflight Simulator or Simple Rockets. They\u0027re similar to KSP but are designed and optimised to work on mobile devices.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Spacescifi","CreatedById":197504,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-10-26T20:50:26Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223873055\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022197711\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221603732988\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022183830\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022RealKerbal3x\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 hours ago, RealKerbal3x said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAside from processing power, another issue is controls - how exactly are you going to fit all of KSP\u0027s controls onto a mobile phone screen?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/207817-spaceman50/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022207817\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/207817-spaceman50/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Spaceman50\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0I\u0027d recommend you check out Spaceflight Simulator or Simple Rockets. They\u0027re similar to KSP but are designed and optimised to work on mobile devices.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nPerhaps this is absurd, but some folks who are serious enough would plug a portable keyboard to their \u0027computer\u0027....I mean phone\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBarring that? Voice control might become good enough, and simplified phone controls along with that.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nJust guessing.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222020-10-26T20:51:04Z\u0022 title=\u002210/26/2020 08:51  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00223 yr\u0022\u003EOctober 26, 2020\u003C/time\u003E by Spacescifi\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Popestar","CreatedById":192906,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-10-26T20:57:53Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223873160\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022197711\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221603745426\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022197504\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Spacescifi\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n6 minutes ago, Spacescifi said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nPerhaps this is absurd, but some folks who are serious enough would plug a portable keyboard to their \u0027computer\u0027....I mean phone\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBarring that? Voice control might become good enough, and simplified phone controls along with that.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nJust guessing.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027m waiting for it to be available via Oculus Quest.\u00A0 Yeah, VR, baby!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"RealKerbal3x","CreatedById":183830,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-10-26T21:02:15Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223873160\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022197711\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221603745426\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022197504\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Spacescifi\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n5 minutes ago, Spacescifi said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nPerhaps this is absurd, but some folks who are serious enough would plug a portable keyboard to their \u0027computer\u0027....I mean phone\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBarring that? Voice control might become good enough, and simplified phone controls along with that.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nJust guessing.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhat if you\u0027re on the train, or other public space, and you want to play some KSP on your phone to pass the time? You obviously don\u0027t have enough space to plug a keyboard into your phone, and people are going to look at you funny if you say something like \u0027Decrease throttle to 50%\u0027 out loud. At that point, why not just wait until you get home to play KSP on your considerably more powerful PC?\u00A0\u003Cspan\u003EThe entire point of a mobile version of KSP (IMO) would be the ability to play on the go\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Corona688","CreatedById":2511,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-10-26T22:01:24Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223873035\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022197711\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221603731150\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022207817\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Spaceman50\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n5 hours ago, Spaceman50 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nCan you play KSP on mobile i mean i play it on my pc but i want to play it when i head to school\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAre you serious?\u00A0 No.\u00A0 How would you play KSP on a one-button controller?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Spaceman50","CreatedById":207817,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-10-28T00:55:59Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nUm i don\u0027t maybe you do 2 controls instead of one!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Spaceman50","CreatedById":207817,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-10-28T00:57:03Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223873160\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022197711\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221603745426\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022197504\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Spacescifi\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 10/26/2020 at 2:50 PM, Spacescifi said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nPerhaps this is absurd, but some folks who are serious enough would plug a portable keyboard to their \u0027computer\u0027....I mean phone\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBarring that? Voice control might become good enough, and simplified phone controls along with that.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nJust guessing.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nwell i do have spaceflight simulator but i perfer ksp\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Yeeter","CreatedById":207892,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-10-31T02:59:07Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf you have GeForce NOW you can play anything on mobile \u003Cspan\u003E:P\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003EMay not be easy but it\u0027s possible. I\u0027m pretty sure you can \u0022bind keys\u0022 to parts of the screen and whatnot with it. Though building a rocket or something efficiently may be a bit difficult.\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Gargamel","CreatedById":64714,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-10-31T11:01:59Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223875348\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022197711\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221604113147\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022207892\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Yeeter\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n8 hours ago, Yeeter said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf you have GeForce NOW you can play anything on mobile \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:P\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/kerbal-forum-uploads/emoticons/default_k_tongue.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:P\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAs of July, KSP is no longer on GFN.\u00A0\u00A0\u00A0 So no, you can\u0027t play anything on mobile.\u00A0\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}